Class BigMap<K,​V extends Set<K>>

java.lang.Object
BigMap<K,​V>
public class BigMap<K,​V extends Set<K>> extends Object
Replacement for map Handles the data for the infection simulation, ensuring thread saftey at every level. Mainly for error handling, trying not to throw. Mike Yang Aug 8
